---
// "Four tools, one toolkit" section showing what Skotch replaces.
---

<div class="not-content replaces-section">
  <h2 class="replaces-heading">One Toolchain to Rule Them All</h2>
  <p class="replaces-subtext">Skotch will replace four separate collections of build tools with a single binary.</p>

  <div class="replaces-grid">

    <div class="replaces-card">
      <div class="replaces-card-top">
        <h3 class="replaces-card-title">Kotlin Compiler</h3>
        <span class="replaces-badge badge-kotlinc">replaces kotlinc</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="replaces-list">
        <li>Lexer, parser, type checker, and MIR all written in Rust</li>
        <li>No JVM startup cost on every compilation</li>
        <li>Five output targets: JVM, DEX, LLVM IR, klib, native</li>
        <li>330+ test fixtures validated against kotlinc output</li>
        <li>Built-in LSP server for editor integration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="replaces-card">
      <div class="replaces-card-top">
        <h3 class="replaces-card-title">Gradle Build</h3>
        <span class="replaces-badge badge-gradle">replaces gradle</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="replaces-list">
        <li>Reads <code>build.gradle.kts</code> and <code>settings.gradle.kts</code> directly</li>
        <li>Multi-module project support with dependency ordering</li>
        <li>JVM target: compiles and packages as executable JAR</li>
        <li>Android target: compiles, generates manifest, produces APK</li>
        <li>No daemon process or multi-gigabyte cache</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="replaces-card">
      <div class="replaces-card-top">
        <h3 class="replaces-card-title">Dependency Management</h3>
        <span class="replaces-badge badge-maven">replaces maven</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="replaces-list">
        <li>Resolves <code>project(":lib")</code> inter-module dependencies</li>
        <li>Parses JDK class files from jmods for Java interop</li>
        <li>Reads <code>kotlin-stdlib.jar</code> for stdlib resolution</li>
        <li>Automatic topological sort of module compilation order</li>
        <li>Maven repository resolution on the roadmap for v0.7</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="replaces-card">
      <div class="replaces-card-top">
        <h3 class="replaces-card-title">Android Packaging</h3>
        <span class="replaces-badge badge-aapt">replaces aapt2</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="replaces-list">
        <li>Generates binary <code>AndroidManifest.xml</code> from build config</li>
        <li>DEX bytecode emitted directly, no <code>d8</code> or <code>r8</code> needed</li>
        <li>APK assembly with correct ZIP alignment</li>
        <li>APK Signature Scheme v2 signing with PEM keys</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .replaces-section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .replaces-heading {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
  }

  .replaces-subtext {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .replaces-subtext {
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
  }

  /* ── Grid ── */

  .replaces-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .replaces-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* ── Card ── */

  .replaces-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    border-radius: 0.875rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 1rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-6);
    position: relative;
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .replaces-card {
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-7, var(--sl-color-gray-6));
  }

  .replaces-card-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .replaces-card-title {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
  }

  /* ── Badge ── */

  .replaces-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--sl-font-mono, ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.3rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .badge-kotlinc {
    background: hsla(265, 50%, 50%, 0.2);
    color: hsl(265, 60%, 70%);
    border: 1px solid hsla(265, 50%, 50%, 0.3);
  }

  .badge-gradle {
    background: hsla(160, 50%, 35%, 0.2);
    color: hsl(160, 55%, 60%);
    border: 1px solid hsla(160, 50%, 35%, 0.3);
  }

  .badge-maven {
    background: hsla(210, 50%, 45%, 0.2);
    color: hsl(210, 55%, 65%);
    border: 1px solid hsla(210, 50%, 45%, 0.3);
  }

  .badge-aapt {
    background: hsla(30, 55%, 45%, 0.2);
    color: hsl(30, 60%, 65%);
    border: 1px solid hsla(30, 55%, 45%, 0.3);
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .badge-kotlinc {
    background: hsla(265, 55%, 55%, 0.12);
    color: hsl(265, 50%, 45%);
    border-color: hsla(265, 50%, 55%, 0.25);
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .badge-gradle {
    background: hsla(160, 55%, 35%, 0.12);
    color: hsl(160, 45%, 32%);
    border-color: hsla(160, 50%, 35%, 0.25);
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .badge-maven {
    background: hsla(210, 55%, 45%, 0.12);
    color: hsl(210, 45%, 38%);
    border-color: hsla(210, 50%, 45%, 0.25);
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .badge-aapt {
    background: hsla(30, 60%, 45%, 0.12);
    color: hsl(30, 50%, 35%);
    border-color: hsla(30, 55%, 45%, 0.25);
  }

  /* ── List ── */

  .replaces-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0 0 0 1.125rem;
    list-style: disc;
  }

  .replaces-list li {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    margin: 0.25rem 0;
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .replaces-list li {
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
  }

  .replaces-list code {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.1rem 0.3rem;
    border-radius: 0.2rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-1);
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .replaces-list code {
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-6);
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
  }
</style>
